      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KEEP ROLLING (4) could manage only second last time but ran useful time (29.44) at Sandown over 515m when beaten 2.5 lengths in a Grade 5. Smart effort latest and looks a key chance again here. DEVIL'S SYMPATHY (3) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive three back in his flying 25.70 win at Warragul over 460m. Expected to feature on best figures. LEKTRA BETA (2) is generally an honest type in the frame at 10 of 30 starts but missed the placings last time when sixth (25.59) over 450m at this track. Solid record at the distance winning five races. Will go close here with a clear run. PAW LAMPADES (8) should be thereabouts.",
